org.openimaj.tools.faces

Interface FaceSimilarityTool.ImageGetter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    Enclosing class:
    FaceSimilarityTool

    public static interface FaceSimilarityTool.ImageGetter<T>
    An interface to get images and names from a list of things. This allows us to pass in a list of stuff and compare against them without having to assume what the stuff is until later.
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
